snippet.title: Magical Eyes - Red is for Anguish Opening
snippet.description:
Opening movie for Magical Eyes - Red is for Anguish with English subtitles.

Coming soon on Steam!
http://steamcommunity.com/app/366780

Opening song "Good Morning!!" by Naokiee Show, animation by Rabbit MACHINE.

Magical Eyes - Red is for Anguish is a mystery visual novel developed by POMERA Studios. 
http://www.pomeswi.com/

Localized into English and published by Fruitbat Factory.
http://fruitbatfactory.com/
